query: SELECT purchaseId, orderNumber, COUNT(*) as cnt FROM pendingMatches pm JOIN purchases p ON pm.purchaseId = p.id WHERE pm.status = 'pending' GROUP BY purchaseId, orderNumber HAVING cnt > 1 LIMIT 5
